1. We cannot override a method with final keyword.
2. All the methods within a final class cannot be overridden as final class cannot be inherited or cannot be parent.
3. final keyword is used to store constant value.

==========================================================================
Static method can be inherited.
Static methods cannot be overridden.
Ex: main method can be overloaded and inherited, but can't be overridden.
=> So method hiding is having same static method in both parent and child class and these methods are completely independent of each other.
1. Overloading of static method is possible, but overriding isn't possible
